{"tid":748011,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[R痕] 歐盟斥Google Android壟斷 罰392億","createTime":"2018-07-19T01:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T07:04:47.000Z","uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5691ca7cb939706e1b22b038a10e7290e181f67c","tid":748011,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:22:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>歐盟斥Google Android壟斷 罰392億</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180719/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180719%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=11d3af79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle推出的智能手機（圖）及平板電腦作業系統Android被指壟斷，昨被歐盟罰款破紀錄的43億歐元（約392億港元）；若90天內不結束違法行為，會有額外罰款，Google表明上訴。<br />\n綑綁式合作惹不滿<br />\n<br />\n歐盟競爭事務專員韋斯塔蓋（Margrethe Vestager）在聲明指，Google自2011年起利用Android鞏固市場領先地位，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求南韓三星及中國華為等手機大牌作「綑綁式合作」</span>，在Android產品<span style=\"color: red;\">預先安裝旗下搜尋器及Chrome網頁瀏覽器，才能使用Google Play等專用程式</span>，有礙競爭，影響消費者利益。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle否認指控，反稱做法為所有人提供更多選擇。2013年投訴Google的商界團體「公平搜索」（FairSearch）歡迎裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">外界最初估計款額會達Google母公司去年1,100億美元（8,580億港元）收入一成；如今罰款只等同公司約兩周收入，以其1,029億美元（約8,000億港元）的財政儲備，對營運影響不大。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAndroid是全球最多人用的智能手機系統，85%手機都選用這套免費軟件，Google則從手機程式廣告圖利。Google非首次被歐盟追打，去年因在網上搜尋器上優先列出旗下購物服務，罰款24.2億歐元（220億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n南韓三星及中國華為呢舖點拆, 比 EU 放左上枱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b391dc0e3ec164aef39ca6dce90d6550aca0b47f","tid":748011,"uid":30510,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"又唔係禁止你裝其他<br />\n咁都壟斷？"},{"pid":"bb500b2d243b03d87d077f5bd3f03e6dfe4147af","tid":748011,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c262e614071b64d29309b55eab0351786576f97","tid":748011,"uid":15410,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"EU班乞衣唔夠錢養難民咪問你拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1675f7818986fa69bf99e2275e5b1d8d88cb4ff1","tid":748011,"uid":75193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次無錢就charge人"},{"pid":"91c1193225e8607300baf9c114cfbed085ce8052","tid":748011,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5140cf2d0e8675f8ad5de2d66091091516ea1897","tid":748011,"uid":28558,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:39:16.000Z","msg":"罰得咁輕"},{"pid":"84eb247235ff0245c1f9142eca48100456003beb","tid":748011,"uid":8014,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"b391dc0e3ec164aef39ca6dce90d6550aca0b47f","tid":748011,"uid":30510,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"又唔係禁止你裝其他<br />\n咁都壟斷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"歐盟：呢期手頭緊，送幾億黎洗下"},{"pid":"2125d143c90a6f66b91f6fdea9c9e20ab3614d4a","tid":748011,"uid":100131,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢set到可以畀人刪已經夠。<br />\n我唔用google music, google video, Duo, 但唔刪得"},{"pid":"407b979bba829042124c5c29bd7c7519d733a3e0","tid":748011,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"同windows N版一樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\"